00:53:07,479 --> 00:53:11,082
   

783
00:53:58,699 --> 00:54:01,158
Where did he go?

784
00:54:09,139 --> 00:54:10,722
Kang Baek.

785
00:54:12,448 --> 00:54:14,420
Kang Baek.

786
00:54:14,420 --> 00:54:16,119
Kang Baek!

787
00:54:22,018 --> 00:54:24,766
Hye Ryul! What's wrong?

788
00:54:24,766 --> 00:54:27,917
Kang Baek... He's on the rooftop.

789
00:54:52,918 --> 00:54:53,888
Grandpa!

790
00:54:53,888 --> 00:54:55,318
Stay in your room.

791
00:54:55,318 --> 00:54:56,758
- Butler Yang. 
 - Yes.

